Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.06,0:00:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s a pleasure to relate to you two aspects
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.69,0:00:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,of the Teaching Committee’s work.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.07,0:00:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,First, what does it take
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.20,0:00:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,to put a regional convention \Ntogether these days?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.91,0:00:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And second, what can we expect \Nwith regard to our midweek meetings?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.70,0:00:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The Teaching Committee is very grateful \Nto every Bethel department.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.33,0:00:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Each of you has contributed in some way
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.09,0:00:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,to the spiritually festive events
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.34,0:00:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,that we enjoy at our conventions \Nand our midweek meetings.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.51,0:00:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Our conventions \Nhave come a long way since 1889.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.10,0:00:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But as you’ll see, the improvements \Nmust be attributed to Jehovah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.73,0:00:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,This convention is so beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.53,0:00:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It moves you to the core.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.95,0:00:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s a very spiritually enriching \Nexperience for all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.70,0:00:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We really see \Nthe Governing Body is caring for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.54,0:00:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.70,0:01:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,This sentiment \Nhas been echoed for over a century.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.79,0:01:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,How is it that year after year people \Nwho have been in the truth for decades
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.05,0:01:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,can say that the most recent convention
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.42,0:01:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,has surpassed all preceding ones?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.34,0:01:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And how do the brothers \Nwho prepare convention programs feel
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.72,0:01:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,when they hear comments like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.39,0:01:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If this were merely the work of humans,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.56,0:01:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,they might feel like Caleb as depicted \Nin the 2017 regional conventions.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.61,0:01:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Thankfully, this is not the work of one man.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.70,0:01:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,All praise goes to Jehovah \Nfor the timely conventions we enjoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.16,0:01:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,His spirit is working through \Nmany willing volunteers.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.00,0:01:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s take a brief look \Nat how our conventions are made.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.21,0:01:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It all begins with the theme.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.71,0:01:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,As Brother Morris pointed out \Nat the 2017 regional convention,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.34,0:01:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,one-word themes \Nare determined years in advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.64,0:02:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That one word will guide \Nthose preparing the program.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.02,0:02:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Dramas \N—the most labor-intensive part of a program—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.56,0:02:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,are developed five years in advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.61,0:02:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,To prepare scripts, \Nthe Teaching Committee cooperates closely
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.65,0:02:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,with the Writing Department \Nin working with a team
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.15,0:02:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,known as the Drama Review Group.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.95,0:02:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,These experienced writers
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.95,0:02:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,develop Scriptural plots \Nthat teach lessons in harmony
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.16,0:02:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,with the convention theme.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.92,0:02:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Scripts are extensively researched
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.08,0:02:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and then sent to Audio/Video Services,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.96,0:02:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,or AVS, for production.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.42,0:02:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,All of this work has to begin early.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.64,0:02:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But how is the rest \Nof a convention program developed?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.89,0:02:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Each year, the Teaching Committee \Ncarefully considers reports
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.27,0:02:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,from around the world \Nfrom Branch Committees
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.56,0:02:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and world headquarters representatives.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.81,0:02:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Often, such reports indicate topics \Nthat could be addressed on a convention.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.78,0:02:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The Teaching Committee \Nthen selects a more specific theme
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.45,0:02:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,that will serve as the basis \Nfor addressing the needs
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.74,0:03:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,of our worldwide brotherhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.66,0:03:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The theme is submitted \Nto the entire Governing Body for approval.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.67,0:03:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, work begins on Scripture themes \Nfor each day of the convention.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.01,0:03:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The Friday program lays the foundation:
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.22,0:03:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the central truth under discussion?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.76,0:03:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Why should we give attention to it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.81,0:03:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Saturday brings admonition \Non personal conduct,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.60,0:03:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,field ministry, and family life.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.85,0:03:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Sunday often highlights what the Bible says
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.48,0:03:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,about our future \Nand encourages us to maintain our hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.69,0:03:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Once this general framework is established,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.99,0:03:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,talks are conceived
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.70,0:03:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,and additional lines of reasoning are chosen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.83,0:03:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Attention is given to how to present ideas
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.16,0:03:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,in a variety of ways:
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.58,0:03:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Could a Scriptural discussion \Nreach the heart more effectively
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.50,0:03:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,by means of an interview or a video?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.38,0:03:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,This detailed sketch is all worked out
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.01,0:04:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,before the Teaching Committee \Nassigns teams of writers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.81,0:04:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,AVS collaborates with the writers \Nin the development of brief videos.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.64,0:04:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The Art Department brainstorms ideas
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.69,0:04:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,for convention branding.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.61,0:04:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The compiler follows \Nthe written content through 70 steps
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.82,0:04:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,of research, fact-checking, and proofreading.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.74,0:04:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, all of these outlines and scripts \Nhave to be translated
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.79,0:04:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,into the 343 languages \Nin which we hold regional conventions.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.54,0:04:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Translation Services \Nhelps teams around the world
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.92,0:04:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,to overcome challenges with the text.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.46,0:04:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Composers and arrangers
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.47,0:04:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,make music tracks for the 18 songs
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.63,0:04:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,that have been selected \Nand the 6 music-video preludes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.64,0:04:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Music services also produces and records
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.72,0:04:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,musical scores \Nfor the feature film, the audio drama,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.69,0:04:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and some 40 other brief videos \Nthat are used on the program.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.61,0:04:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But the Teaching Committee’s involvement
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.74,0:05:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn’t end here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.74,0:05:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It provides direction \Nregarding the assigning of speakers,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.66,0:05:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,the design of sound systems,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.70,0:05:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,the securing of contracts \Nfor hotels and venues,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.87,0:05:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,the operation of convention departments,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.88,0:05:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and the training of volunteers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.21,0:05:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Thousands of willing workers are involved,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.13,0:05:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,each submitting to the inspired direction
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.38,0:05:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,in God’s Word and the influence
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.97,0:05:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,of his holy spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.43,0:05:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The benefits of such collaboration are felt
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.52,0:05:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,not only at our annual conventions
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.19,0:05:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,but also at our weekly meetings.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.19,0:05:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s been two years since the inception
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.19,0:05:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,of the Our Christian Life and Ministry \Nmidweek meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.78,0:05:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,How have things been going on that front?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.20,0:05:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything got better: \Nhow the brothers and sisters feel
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.45,0:05:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,about the meeting and how they participate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.70,0:05:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,There are more videos at the meetings,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.79,0:05:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,so I feel closer \Nto the worldwide brotherhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.50,0:05:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I really enjoy what it does for young ones,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.67,0:06:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,especially the two-minute parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.47,0:06:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You see young ones, even very young children, \Ndo a demonstration.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.85,0:06:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of just underlining to prepare,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.10,0:06:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,now I get excited looking for gems.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.43,0:06:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We really dig into a Bible account.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.36,0:06:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I learn a whole lot more.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.65,0:06:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,After the meeting,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.82,0:06:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,we enjoy discussing the gems we discovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.70,0:06:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Every meeting gives \Nyou something practical
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.20,0:06:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,that you can apply \Nthe next weekend right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.20,0:06:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we don’t just read \Nthe Bible as a family,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.08,0:06:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,but we pay more attention \Nto Jehovah’s qualities.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.08,0:06:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Young ones and new publishers \Nare now less hesitant
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.51,0:06:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,about sharing their beliefs at the door
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.51,0:06:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,because they simply do \Nwhat they learned at the meetings.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.39,0:06:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Regarding production of the meeting,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.93,0:06:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,methods of the Gilead School are employed
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.64,0:06:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,in the approach to study.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.98,0:06:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The Gilead approach to study
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.35,0:06:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,considers context, explanation,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.11,0:07:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and application.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.11,0:07:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Analyzing the context \Nconsiders the time period,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.61,0:07:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,the historical setting, \Nand the writer’s intent.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.78,0:07:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,These are built \Ninto the Treasures From God’s Word
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.20,0:07:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and the Bible Book Introduction Videos
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.25,0:07:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,we see at the midweek meetings.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.00,0:07:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The explanations for the verses \Nare all based on the publications
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.17,0:07:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,of “the faithful and discreet slave”
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.17,0:07:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,to ensure accuracy and correct understanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.59,0:07:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, at Gilead School, \Nstudents aren’t allowed to guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.60,0:07:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Once a scripture is explained accurately,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.81,0:07:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,then it can be applied properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.69,0:07:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,This method of context and explanation
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.73,0:07:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,followed by application \Nleads to meaningful Bible study.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.74,0:07:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The Service Committee Office
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.86,0:07:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,provides input on field service presentations \Nand Living as Christians.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.24,0:07:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The Writing Department gives insight \Non how to feature our publications.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.54,0:08:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What will change after January?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.96,0:08:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,As announced at the 2017 annual meeting,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.71,0:08:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,the public edition \Nof The Watchtower will be published
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.30,0:08:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,three times a year instead of six.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.93,0:08:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The same will be true for Awake!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.35,0:08:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, specific monthly literature offers \Nhave been discontinued.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.23,0:08:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Thus, we will enjoy some adjustments \Nin our field service presentations.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.73,0:08:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,As you will see, the new focus will be
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.24,0:08:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,not so much on publications
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.57,0:08:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,but on conversations.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.20,0:08:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Clearly, the production \Nof our midweek meetings
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.24,0:08:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and regional conventions \Ntakes a lot of planning
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.29,0:08:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,and the cooperation of many willing workers
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.33,0:08:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,in a variety of Bethel departments.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.21,0:08:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But the positive effects \Nare felt around the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.22,0:08:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,All I can say to Jehovah is, \N“Thank you, Jehovah, for letting me be here.”
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.05,0:08:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel very grateful \Nto Jehovah for the meetings.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.93,0:09:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Jehovah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.77,0:09:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes Bethel receives letters \Nthat go something like this:
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.90,0:09:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,“Thank you for your tireless efforts.”
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.32,0:09:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, the brothers and sisters \Nworking on all these projects are tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.82,0:09:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But they never tire
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.83,0:09:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,of trusting in and cooperating with the One \Nwho truly is tireless:
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.70,0:09:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,the Source of all divine instruction, \NJehovah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.71,0:09:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,He alone can replace copper with gold,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.04,0:09:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,so that each segment of divine education
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.92,0:09:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,truly is the best ever.
